---
title: Hearty Broccoli Cheddar Chowder with Potatoes & Scallions
description: Get this hearty, comforting bowl of creamy deliciousness on the table in just 25 minutes! While potatoes and broccoli cook until tender, you’ll make a deeply flavorful broth with garlic and scallions, then add our signature cheese roux base to make a rich, luscious soup. Once you add the veggies, mustard, and cheddar, it’s go time. Grab your favorite spoon for this cozy, satisfying chowda you’ll be prouda!
